			"remarks": {
				"p": "The following controls represent the \n\t\t\t\tS2C2F v1.1 (https://github.com/ossf/s2c2f/blob/main/specification/framework.md) for the purposes of assessing secure development pracices in alignment with S2C2F requirements for a given software project or product*. Copyrights for this work are held by the Linux Foundation Open Source Security Foundation (OpenSSF)."
			}
		},
		"groups": {
